parameters.name: レクイエム・暗い場面

parameters: \n<Village chief>"Ameria, do you understand the gravity of the situation?"

\n<Village chief>"With the Valam guards gone, our village is literally
defenseless. We're sitting ducks for monsters, not to
mention bandits."

\n<Village chief>"Because of you... because of you, the lives of everyone in
this village are in danger. How do you plan to take
responsibility?"

\n<Villager b>"We don't even have a doctor! What are we supposed to do if
someone gets hurt?"

\n<Villager b>"You still dare to say that! I don't want to be treated by
someone like you!"

\n<Ameria>"But... I can treat them properly... I can be of use to
everyone..."

\n<Village chief>"Ameria, please don't make this any harder... You're a
nuisance."

\n<Village chief>"I've held my tongue out of respect for Luerre-san, but it's
clear now... nothing good comes from letting outsiders in."

\n<Villagers>"That's right! Get out! You're causing trouble for
everyone," "This isn't your home!"
\n<??>"...So noisy. All you do is cry."

\n<Lyric>"Hello there, I'm an outsider too♪ I've been taken care of
here for a reason. Don't be so wary. I'll be leaving soon
enough."

\n<Lyric>"Besides... I don't know what happened, but can you stop
making such a fuss? It's unbearably noisy."

\n<Village chief>"...If you know nothing, then don't meddle, outsider. This
is our village's problem!"

\n<Lyric>"This sister is an outsider too, right? Then I'm in the same
boat. Let me join the club."

\n<Lyric>"...Besides, village problems or whatever, I couldn't care
less."

\n<Lyric>"I don't like seeing someone who took care of me being made
to cry right before my eyes. If you keep this up, I might
just cause a scene before I leave."
\n<Villager a>"Village chief! This woman, she's using magic...!"

\n<Village chief>"Hmm... Everyone, let's return. We can't afford any trouble
right now."

\n<Village chief>"I don't know who you are or where you're from, but please
don't do anything strange in this village. We don't want any
more problems."
\n<Village chief>"And... both of you, leave this place quickly. Understood?"

\n<Lyric>"It's nothing. You were just crying so loudly it was
annoying."

\n<Lyric>"Well, if you don't want to talk about it, that's fine. I'm
not really interested anyway."

\n<Lyric>"More importantly, you can't stay here anymore, right? So
you'll let me out now, won't you?"

\n<Lyric>"What, you want me to stay here alone? If you do that, I'll
burn down this church and kill you as well."

\n<Ameria>"...Then, will you come with me to the mainland? I think
it's safe there since the priest is also there."
\n<Lyric>"Hah? You're joking. Who would go with someone like you?"

\n<Lyric>"Sorry, but I'm taking the robe that was in the room. I
don't know who's after me, but just to be cautious."
\n<Lyric>"...Now, let's have you remove the barrier."
\n<Lyric>"I don't care about you. Hurry up."
\n<Lyric>"Is it undone...? Finally, I can get out."
ローゼリッテ_非戦闘_通常
